  特殊布线命令，用于连接电源地网络到特定的物理对象，如模块引脚、焊盘引脚、电源环等。

  调用参数: -connect { blockPin corePin } -nets {VDD GND} -layerChangeRange {M1(1) M8(8)} -crossoverViaLayerRange {M1 M8} -targetViaLayerRange {M1 M8} -blockPinTarget { nearestRingStripe nearestTarget } -checkAlignedSecondaryPin 1 -blockPin useLef -allowJogging 1 -allowLayerChange 1
